    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle represents an exceptional opportunity for a buyer seeking reliability and style without the showroom price tag. The exterior paint retains a brilliant shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has been kept in a smoke-free environment. The premium upholstery is in great shape, showing only slight creasing on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. All technological features, including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and driver-assist sensors, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. It has been serviced regularly at factory intervals, with a recent brake pad replacement and a fresh oil change. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring many miles of worry-free driving. This car has been garaged nightly and reflects the pride of ownership of a single-owner household.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
