      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks fantastic on the road? I\u2019m parting with this beauty, and it\u2019s in really solid shape. It\u2019s been well-loved, runs super smoothly, and is totally ready for its next adventure with you! It\u2019s such a great find for anyone wanting a quality car without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself\u2014I'd love to find it a great new home!",
